      "review_title": "I love it",
      "review_description": "Lethal Ape 3 is one of my favorite VR games because it’s immersive, intense, and incredibly fun. Being in VR makes every moment feel real, and the atmosphere keeps you on edge the entire time.\nThe monsters are easily the best part of the game. Each one feels unique, scary, and unpredictable, which makes every playthrough exciting. Even when it’s terrifying, it’s still fun, and that balance is what makes the game special.\nOverall, Lethal Ape 3 is a VR game I genuinely love, especially because of its monsters and immersive experience.",
